Title: Electrochemical Detection of Nitrate
Description: This project aims to develop a low cost, user friendly, accurate, and portable device for the electrochemical detection of nitrate in drinking water for use in developing countries where this problem is prevalent.
Location: Learning Commons 133, Viewing and Taping B

Title: Biological Applications of Scanning Thermal Microscopy
Description: Our team is using AppNano Vertisense SThM probes to characterize gold nanoparticles, as well as other biologically relevant materials.
Location: Learning Commons 133, Viewing and Taping B
